  <title><literal>ICES()</literal></title>

  <indexterm significance="preferred">
    <primary>Dialplan-Applikationen</primary>

    <secondary><code>ICES()</code></secondary>
  </indexterm>

  <simpara>Streams the active channel to IceCast server.</simpara>

  <synopsis>ICES(<replaceable>config_file.xml</replaceable>)</synopsis>

  <simpara>Sends an audio stream of the active channel to an IceCast<indexterm>
      <primary>IceCast</primary>
    </indexterm> server.<footnote>
      <para><ulink
      url="http://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Icecast">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Icecast</ulink></para>
    </footnote>. For a sample <replaceable>config_file.xml</replaceable> see
  <filename>contrib/asterisk-ices.xml</filename>.</simpara>

